text:
Heads up Target Shoppers! Starting April 2nd, Target will be offering a a Target coupon valid for a FREE $20 Target Gift Card with a select baby department purchase of $125 or more! This coupon will be available in the weekly ad OR you should also be able to find this coupon on the Cartwheel app or by texting SAVE to 827438 to have it delivered to your smartphone (starting 4/2).
This offer will also be available online at Target.com . Please note, this offer includes diapers, wipes, training pants, baby formula, baby food and toiletries. And to sweeten the deal even further, you will also be able to earn a FREE $10 Target Gift Card with each purchase of 2 select diaper packs (starting 4/2)!
Target Deal Ideas (Starting 4/2): Buy 4 Pampers Swaddlers Diapers Superpacks $24.29 each 
Buy 2 Pampers Baby Dry Diaper Superpacks $24.29 each 
Total = $145.74
Scan the FREE $20 Target Gift Card with select baby department purchase of $125 or more coupon found in the ad, on the Cartwheel app or by texting SAVE to 827438 
And use four $2/1 Pampers Swaddlers Diapers printable coupons (will need access to 2 computers)
And use two $2/1 Pampers Baby Dry Diapers printable coupons 
Pay $133.74
Get back a FREE $20 Target Gift Card (for scanning above coupon)
Get back three FREE $10 Target Gift Cards (for buying 6 select diaper packs)
